{"tid":2373422,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"東區醫院發生嚴重醫療事故 駁錯心肺機31分鐘 病人通波仔後危殆","createTime":"2021-01-20T12:25:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T14:39:26.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2a87a417b0decbe94fdd1ac36b63f2c3cfb5352a","tid":2373422,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T12:25:56.000Z","msg":"東區醫院發生嚴重醫療事故。一名醫生施行緊急「通波仔」手術時，發現病人血壓不穩，為病人接駁人工心肺機，但竟調轉動脈和靜脈來接駁，31分鐘後才發現出錯。雖然手術順利完成，但病人情況仍然危殆，留醫深切治療部。院方已向病人家屬解釋及致歉，並已通報事故予醫院管理局總部，需於8星期內提交調查報告。<br />\n<br />\n東區醫院發言人表示，一名患心肌梗塞的57歲男病人，1月16日因嚴重氣促和抽搐，送到該院急症室，當時情況危殆，插喉後送往深切治療部。病人2日後心臟一度停頓，醫生急救後安排他接受緊急「通波仔」手術。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210120/VLE2CL7KKJFUVLN7N5KE7F46VY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210120%2FVLE2CL7KKJFUVLN7N5KE7F46VY%2F&d=6tm4WXRLZYcZc%2BeJmW1Ia6zbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=62c41eb5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210120%2FVLE2CL7KKJFUVLN7N5KE7F46VY%2F&h=54c2fad4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210120/VLE2CL7KKJFUVLN7N5KE7F46VY/</a>"},{"pid":"21f6fdb19b5f66d865d6df90093b78001723f2cc","tid":2373422,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T12:28:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n錯到咁"},{"pid":"42971a140c77fc83f377e91168328645b21e171c","tid":2373422,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T12:34:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d9aaf42a228041a66d3e23